entries.title_d: Capture Saysmond Varg, a known Black Sun assassin wanted in connection to attacks on Naboo citizens
entries.title: Dantooine System: Capture a Black Sun Assassin
entries.taunt_5: Hide behind your hostage RSF fool, they will not save you.
entries.taunt_4: Hide behind your hostage RSF fool, they will not save you.
entries.taunt_3: Hide behind your hostage RSF fool, they will not save you.
entries.taunt_2: He would welcome death over capture!
entries.taunt_1: Hide behind your hostage RSF fool, they will not save you.
entries.target_disabled: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Target has successfully been disabled. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Priority Alert! Priority Alert!  Preliminary scans indicate that the target Saysmond Varg was not on the Dru`Mdar. Proceed to following patrol route and await orders. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.recovery_success: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Good job pilot, Saysmond Varg is on his way to RSF custody now. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_recover_d: Pull up close to begin the capture protocol
entries.quest_location_d: Area of friendly control in the Dantooine System, this assassin was either brave, or stupid.
entries.quest_escort_d: Escort the Dru'Mdar into position for a hyperspace jump
entries.quest_disable_d: Target the Dru'Mdar's engines to disable it
entries.failed_escape: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Drats, Saymonz has eluded us again. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.failed_destroy: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Damn, we needed that vessel intact, Saymonz would have been a bonus. > \#pcontrast3
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tacitcal Computer: < \#pcontrast1 The Dru`Mdar escort has been wiped out, proceed with primary objective. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer < \#pcontrast1 An escort has been destroyed, %DI remain in the Dru`Mdar escort \#pcontrast3 >
entries.complete: I appear to be at your mercy, Captain.  Shall we get moving then?
entries.capture_complete: Ship systems have been captured, setting autopilot for jump to hyperspace.
entries.attack_notify: Enemy craft detected on attack vector.
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 A vessel matching the description of the Dru`Mdar has appeared with escort.  Preparing systems for combat. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: <\#pcontrast1 Stay alert, Saymonz Varg is expected any moment \#pcontrast3>
entries.angry_disable: Do you really think you have won?
entries.abort: You let the Varg get away, this is most distressing.
